node.text:
Visit @SculptMovements 💕 for workouts, routine, and everythin else you eed to become fit! .
Treino de MMI com 01. Agachamento máquina 15/12/10 + drop com extensora 4 x 4 / 4x3 / 4x2 /4x 1 aumentando a carga ( 1 série ) 
1 x 10 com pico de contração em cima + 10 saindo da inércia 
1 x 10 com excêntrica lenta + 10 concêntrica lenta + 10 
02. Stiff 3 x 15 + bom dia 10 
03. Flexora 9 x 6 alternando a carga entre leva e pesado 
1 x 30 curtas + 10 isometria + 12 
1 x unilateral 8 /7/6 até zerar sem intervalo 
04. Flexora em pé 3 x 12 parando no meio + glúteo no cabo 3 x 12 
Panturrilhas sempre 😅
Macacão @santtaloren
.
.
.
Credit @graoficial #Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

NO EQUIPMENT LEGS AT HOME ✨ Save & @SculptMobility for daily pain management, flexibility, and workout advice📚 
.
Grab your gorgeous self and some motivation because that’s all you’re going to need for this home leg routine 💫 Concentrate on feeling the muscle and don’t rush through the sets 💪🏼 This is perfect for beginners or if your home gym is missing some weights 🤗 Let’s go!!!
.
ROUTINE:
1️⃣ Squat to calf raise 3 x 15
2️⃣ Alternating reverse lunge to squat 3 x 8 per side
3️⃣ Side lunge to squat jump 3 x 8 per side
4️⃣ Lateral squat slide 3 x 15 per side

🎶 "Gente En Havana" - Camila Cabello/Daddy Yankee x J Balvin/Willy William - PaulGMashups 
credit @mssannamaria
